Subject: Queer: Identity, Sexuality and Beyond
Description: Queer means so many thing to so many people: gender identity, orientation, even a political statement of who you are. Let's talk about the range of identities that fall under the queer label.  Speakers include:Jen Schwartz, Matt Sweet, Max Issac, Allison Demars, Ryan Souder - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Sexual Safety
Description: Come with all your questions about sex and safety, and we'll talk about how to keep safe and stay healthy! This panel is for ages 18+ only. Minors are not allowed (with or without a parent).  Speakers include:Jen Schwartz, Matt Sweet, Max Issac, Allison Demars, Ryan Souder - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: The Art of Negotiating
Description: From negotiating a scene to negotiating a relationship, come learn some great lessons in the art of negotiation. This panel is for ages 18+ only. Minors are not allowed (with or without a parent).  Speakers include:Jen Schwartz, Allison Demars, Ryan Souder - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: LGBTQ Identities
Description: Let's talk about LGBQT identities  Speakers include:Jen Schwartz, Matt Sweet, Max Issac, Mari Brighe, Allison Demars, Ryan Souder - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Beyond the Binary
Description: Let's look into our own personal identities beyond the gender binary.  Speakers include:Jen Schwartz, Matt Sweet, Max Issac, Allison Demars, Ryan Souder - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes
